e restrictions for the women players.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age restrictions\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"the women players\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is only one of the many gender-based differences in how men and women athletes compete at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the many gender-based differences\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"men and women athletes\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My research examines how the International Olympic Committee (IOC) has promoted gender equality at the Games.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My research\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"gender equality\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My bookGender Equality and the Olympic Programmefocuses on the sport programme - all the sports and events included at the Games - because it is the most visible aspect of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My bookGender\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"Equality\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Programmefocuses\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport programme\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"all the sports\", 