, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"one strategy\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"foster gender equality\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Claims about achieving \\\"gender balance\\\" have been an integral part of all the IOC's statements about Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2819, \"end\": 2822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.227064412436472e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2842, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.75926398749874e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Claims\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"gender balance\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2779}, {\"ngram\": \"an integral part\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is crucial to critically examine what these claims mean and how they relate to achieving gender equality.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these claims\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"gender equality\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ensuring gender parity - the same number of men and women athletes and men's and women's events - is important for gender equality at the Games, but it does not address the conditions of men's and women's participation.\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gender parity\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"the same number\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"men and women athletes\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3030}, {\"ngram\": \"men's and women's events\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3059}, {\"ngram\": \"gender equality\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3094}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"men's and women's participation\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC'saim to achieve gender balancereveals an incomplete, numbers-focused commitment to gender equality.\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3292, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gender balancereveals\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"an incomplete, numbers-focused commitment\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3272}, {\"ngram\": \"gender equality\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When men and women compete in the same sports, international federations continue to enforce differences between men's and women's events.\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3302}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3312}, {\"ngram\": \"the same sports\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3339}, {\"ngram\": \"international federations\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3366}, {\"ngram\": \"differences\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3398}, {\"ngram\": \"men's and women's events\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These differences include: thelength of races;weight categories; theheight, weight, size and spacing of equipment; thesize of venues; and differences injudging,rulesanduniforms.\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These differences\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"thelength\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"races;weight categories\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3496}, {\"ngram\": \"theheight\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3507}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"size\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3521}, {\"ngram\": \"spacing\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3533}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3546}, {\"ngram\": \"thesize\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"differences\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3582}, {\"ngram\": \"rulesanduniforms\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, in artistic gymnastics,the differences between the men's and women's competitionsinclude age requirements (18 years old for men and 16 for women); different apparatus (e.g., parallel bars for men and uneven parallel bars for women); the number of apparatus (six for men and four for women); and uniform requirements (long or short pants for men, leotards or unitards for women).\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 4003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3623}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic gymnastics\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's and women's competitionsinclude age requirements\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3752}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3769}, {\"ngram\": \"different apparatus\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3791}, {\"ngram\": \"(e.g., parallel bars\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3820}, {\"ngram\": \"uneven parallel bars\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3845}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3855}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3868}, {\"ngram\": \"apparatus\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3881}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3894}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"uniform requirements\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"long or short pants\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3961}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"leotards\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 3979}, {\"ngram\": \"unitards\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3991}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the floor and vault - apparatus on which both men and women compete - women's floor routines are set to music and include dance elements, while the men's do not.\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 4008, \"to\": 4017}, {\"ngram\": \"vault - apparatus\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4039}, {\"ngram\": \"both men\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4057}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram\": \"women's floor routines\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4100}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4117}, {\"ngram\": \"dance elements\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4144}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When performing the same skills, men's eligible scores are lower than women's.\", \"from\": 4170, \"to\": 4248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same skills\", \"from\": 4186, \"to\": 4201}, {\"ngram\": \"men's eligible scores\", \"from\": 4203, \"to\": 4224}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4240, \"to\": 4245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What the audience sees is women's gymnastics performed in ways thatemphasize stereotypical femininityand minimize strength and power.\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 4255, \"to\": 4267}, {\"ngram\": \"women's gymnastics\", \"from\": 4276, \"to\": 4294}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4312}, {\"ngram\": \"stereotypical femininityand minimize strength\", \"from\": 4327, \"to\": 4372}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In contrast, men's gymnastics events are organized toemphasize the athletes' strength and power.\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contrast\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4395}, {\"ngram\": \"men's gymnastics events\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4420}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' strength\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4469}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 4474, \"to\": 4479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These gender-based differences are examples of gender inequality.\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These gender-based differences\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4512}, {\"ngram\": \"examples\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"gender inequality\", \"from\": 4529, \"to\": 4546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In cases where sports are gender-differentiated, women's sports are designed to be a lesser version than the men's.\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cases\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4557}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4570}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4612}, {\"ngram\": \"a lesser version\", \"from\": 4632, \"to\": 4648}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 4654, \"to\": 4661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women's races are shorter, there are fewer weight categories, equipment and venues are lighter and smaller and women wear more revealing uniforms.\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women's races\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4678}, {\"ngram\": \"fewer weight categories\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4725}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment\", \"from\": 4727, \"to\": 4736}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4747}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4781}, {\"ngram\": \"more revealing uniforms\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Differences in men's and women's conditions of participation are the result of decisions made by those who control Olympic sports - decision-makerswho continue to be predominantly men.\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Differences\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4824}, {\"ngram\": \"men's and women's conditions\", \"from\": 4828, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"participation\", \"from\": 4860, \"to\": 4873}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 4878, \"to\": 4888}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic sports - decision-makerswho\", \"from\": 4928, \"to\": 4963}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 4993, \"to\": 4996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The differences are not naturally occurring, nor are they universal.\", \"from\": 4998, \"to\": 5066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The differences\", \"from\": 4998, \"to\": 5013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, there are several sports and events on the Olympic programme that are not gender-differentiated.\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 5071, \"to\": 5075}, {\"ngram\": \"several sports\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5101}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 5106, \"to\": 5112}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic programme\", \"from\": 5116, \"to\": 5137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, men and women athletes competing inarcheryandbadmintonuse the same venue, equipment and rules.\", \"from\": 5174, \"to\": 5281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5185}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 5187, \"to\": 5190}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 5195, \"to\": 5200}, {\"ngram\": \"competing inarcheryandbadmintonuse\", \"from\": 5210, \"to\": 5244}, {\"ngram\": \"the same venue\", \"from\": 5245, \"to\": 5259}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment\", \"from\": 5261, \"to\": 5270}, {\"ngram\": \"rules\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is evidence of internal contradictions in the Olympic programme; some events are constructed to be different for men and women athletes, while others are not.\", \"from\": 5283, \"to\": 5446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"evidence\", \"from\": 5291, \"to\": 5299}, {\"ngram\": \"internal contradictions\", \"from\": 5303, \"to\": 5326}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic programme\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5351}, {\"ngram\": \"some events\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5364}, {\"ngram\": \"men and women athletes\", \"from\": 5401, \"to\": 5423}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This reinforces the need to identify and explain the remaining examples of gender-based differences.\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 5463, \"to\": 5471}, {\"ngram\": \"the remaining examples\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5518}, {\"ngram\": \"gender-based differences\", \"from\": 5522, \"to\": 5546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These internal contradictions also require further attention from the IOC and the adoption of a more complete definition of gender equality - one that includes opportunity and status.\", \"from\": 5549, \"to\": 5732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5619, \"end\": 5622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.227064412436472e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These internal contradictions\", \"from\": 5549, \"to\": 5578}, {\"ngram\": \"further attention\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5609}, {\"ngram\": \"the adoption\", \"from\": 5627, \"to\": 5639}, {\"ngram\": \"a more complete definition\", \"from\": 5643, \"to\": 5669}, {\"ngram\": \"gender equality\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5688}, {\"ngram\": \"- one\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5694}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunity\", \"from\": 5709, \"to\": 5720}, {\"ngram\": \"status\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC needs to look beyond the numbers and work with international federations to address athletes' conditions of participation in the same sports.\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5738, \"end\": 5741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.227064412436472e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the numbers\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5774}, {\"ngram\": \"international federations\", \"from\": 5789, \"to\": 5814}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' conditions\", \"from\": 5826, \"to\": 5846}, {\"ngram\": \"participation\", \"from\": 5850, \"to\": 5863}, {\"ngram\": \"the same sports\", \"from\": 5867, \"to\": 5882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Crucially, embracing and enforcing gender equality should not mean using men's sports as the standard (e.g., increasing the length of women's races to be the same as the men's distance).\", \"from\": 5885, \"to\": 6071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gender equality\", \"from\": 5920, \"to\": 5935}, {\"ngram\": \"men's sports\", \"from\": 5958, \"to\": 5970}, {\"ngram\": \"the standard\", \"from\": 5974, \"to\": 5986}, {\"ngram\": \"the length\", \"from\": 6005, \"to\": 6015}, {\"ngram\": \"women's races\", \"from\": 6019, \"to\": 6032}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's distance\", \"from\": 6051, \"to\": 6069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather, this is an opportunity for international federations to determine the best possible conditions for all athletes in their sports.\", \"from\": 6072, \"to\": 6208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 6088, \"to\": 6102}, {\"ngram\": \"international federations\", \"from\": 6107, \"to\": 6132}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible conditions\", \"from\": 6146, \"to\": 6174}, {\"ngram\": \"all athletes\", \"from\": 6179, \"to\": 6191}, {\"ngram\": \"their sports\", \"from\": 6195, \"to\": 6207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2026,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 6210, \"to\": 6264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2026,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 6210, \"to\": 6264}]}]}"